HEADWORD: Treebeard
<hw>Tree"beard`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A pendulous branching lichen (<spn>Usnea barbata</spn>); -- so
called from its resemblance to hair.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

